'''Belizi''', korolen [[''Britania Belizi'']] ye jamana ye min be [[Cema Amerika]]. Ali nayasɔrɔ ko [[Maya ‎Mansamara]] fan dɔ don, Belizi ma deli ka kɛ [[Espanyi Mansamara]] kɔnɔ. Belizi tun nɔrɔlen [[Britania ‎Mansamara]] la kan kɔn yɛrɛta ɳɛ san 1981. Jamana in be danbɔ saheli ni [[Meksik]] ye, tlebi ni ‎‎[[Gatemala]], kɔrɔn ani worodugukɔrɔn ni [[Karaibu]] ye.‎
